text: Rahib Məmmədov (born 22 July 1992 in Baku) is an Azerbaijani hurdler. His personal best is of 14.06 (2018). He won the 110 m hurdles at 2011 European Team Championships. His personal best of 60 m hurdles indoor is the national record. ==References== == External links == *IAAF Athlete’s profile Category:Azerbaijani male athletes Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:European Games competitors for Azerbaijan Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2015 European Games
